ults applied.\n     *\n     * This means that the default [Decoder]s, [Preprocessor]s, [NodeTransformer]s, [ParameterMapper]s,\n     * [PropertySource]s, and [Parser]s are all registered.\n     *\n     * If you wish to avoid adding defaults, for example to avoid certain decoders or sources, then\n     * use [empty] to obtain an empty ConfigLoaderBuilder and call the various addDefault methods manually.\n     */\n    fun defaul\n\n--- com/sksamuel/hoplite/parsers/DefaultParserRegistry.kt\nTraceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"<stdin>\", line 7, in <module>\n  File \"/home/vjovanov/.pyenv/versions/3.11.5/lib/python3.11/zipfile.py\", line 1510, in read\n    with self.open(name, \"r\", pwd) as fp:\n         ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\n  File \"/home/vjovanov/.pyenv/versions/3.11.5/lib/python3.11/zipfile.py\", line 1547, in open\n    zinfo = self.getinfo(name)\n            ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\n  File \"/home/vjovanov/.pyenv/versions/3.11.5/lib/python3.11/zipfile.py\", line 1476, in getinfo\n    raise KeyError(\nKeyError: \"There is no item named 'com/sksamuel/hoplite/parsers/DefaultParserRegistry.kt' in the archive\"\n\n\nCommand exited with code 1"}], "details": {}, "isError": true, "timestamp": 1782548877388}]}
